description:
Adds the ultra weird mini-game "Kanna Raising Simulator" to the EXTRA menu.
Capture a variety of materials to make fertilizer and grow your very own Kanna! 
There are loads of potential Kannas to grow, and you can check out every one
you've completed in "Kanna's Strangallery"!
name: DLC Mini-game "Kanna Raising Simulator"
